@startuml SDUS03

title SSD — Admin views platform analytics (Actor · System)

actor "Admin" as admin
participant ": System" as system

admin -> system : 1: Access Analytics Dashboard
system -> system : 1.1: Query default analytics data (last 30 days)
system --> admin : 1.2: Display dashboard (KPIs, charts, tables)

alt [2 Apply Filter]

    admin -> system : 2: Set filters (date range and/or category)
    system -> system : 2.1: Query analytics data with filters
    system --> admin : 2.2: Refresh dashboard

end

alt [3a Export PDF]

    admin -> system : 3a: Request PDF export
    system -> system : 3a.1: Generate PDF report
    system --> admin : 3a.2: Download PDF file

else [3b Export Excel]

    admin -> system : 3b: Request Excel export
    system -> system : 3b.1: Generate Excel report
    system --> admin : 3b.2: Download Excel file

end

@enduml
